article.headline: Apple Inc. stock rises Wednesday, still underperforms market
article.body: Shares of Apple Inc. Apple Inc. closed $22.90 short of its 52-week high ($137.98), which the company achieved on September 2nd. Cl A GOOGL, +1.82% rose 0.56% to $1,459.14, and International Business Machines Corp. IBM, -2.81% rose 1.72% to $124.07.
